Requirements:
    CMake 2.6 or later
    scons

Build instructions for 64-bit system:

    svn checkout -r 5610 http://v8.googlecode.com/svn/trunk lib
    cd lib && scons mode=release arch=x64
    cd ..
    cmake . && make

Build instructions for 32-bit system:

    svn checkout -r 5610 http://v8.googlecode.com/svn/trunk lib
    cd lib && scons mode=release
    cd ..
    cmake . && make

